TopicTitle: Make a wish... and have it horribly corrupted!

Articles.Content:
Granted, but you never get to see it.

I wish I was good at designing rockets.

Granted, but you do not improve, the skills of everyone one else decrease to the point where you are considered "good"

I wish for potatOS

Granted. You get a computer which is designed for the sole purpose of printing "Potato" on the monitor. It does nothing else.

I wish for infinite potato batteries.

Granted. They give you 0.00000000000000000000000000000000000001 voltz all together.

I wish for wish!

Pine Taradox!

I wish for a 4x4 V12 bicycle, now.

Granted, But it explodes as soon as you start it.

I wish for fish.

Granted, they are piranhas which jump out of the tank and attack you.

I wish people cared more about school.

Granted. You start caring less, which makes them care more by comparison.

I wish for eggs.

Granted, but they are rotten.

I wish I was a student at MIT.
Granted, but there is a shooting and you are of the deceased.

Granted, but I deleted your wish.

I wish for an adult.

Granted, it sends you to an orphanage.

I wish for an Eevee.

Granted, but it evolves into Magieon, an Eevee with all the usefulness of a Magikarp.

I wish for the perfect computer that didn't want to kill or enslave anyone.

granted but, it gave your brain the perfect virus....

I wish for a deathstar

Granted, but the rebels blow it up.

I wish for a pet tiger.

granted -- but it puts you in a cage, locks it and throws away the key:

I wish there were more lolz on this thread.

Granted, but you get confined to 4chan for the rest of your life.

I wish Ion engines worked faster.

Granted, but you get eaten by the deep space kraken every time.

I wish for a deep space sea serpent.
Granted, but it drowns and suffocates at the same time while its blood boils away. I wish for a smarter rocket.

Granted. It's still horribly st00pid.

I wish you didn't have to be cruel to be kind (doo doo doo doo~)

Granted, but I have to be kind to be kind.

I wish that the next poster would bring FEZ 2 back. (Phil Fish rage quitted after some "critics" called him a real bad name.)

Granted, but it's made really quickly and horrible.

I wish for the ISS to be deorbited.

Granted, but a module lands on you.

I wish someone else wished that I wished that other person's friend wished for people to stop wishing about me.

Granted, but I am too tired to read that, so I'll just give you some rotten tuna.

I wish I didn't have insomnia all the time.

Granted, you go into a lifelong coma.
